00:04:15.800 --> 00:04:22.060
I know I should. I know we've tried,
multiple times, and I've let you down.

00:04:22.790 --> 00:04:26.900
I know I should just let you live your
life and I'm fucking everything up

00:04:26.900 --> 00:04:30.860
because i'm being weak and talking to
you like this so Yes I'm trying.

